The data relating to real estate for sale on this website comes in part from the Internet Data Exchange program of MLS NOW. Real estate listings held by brokerage firms other than Zillow, Inc. are marked with the Internet Data Exchange logo and detailed information about them includes the name of the listing broker(s). Zillow, Inc. does not display the entire MLS NOW IDX database on this website. The listings of some real estate brokerage firms have been excluded. Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. The listing broker’s offer of compensation is made only to participants of the MLS where the listing is filed.

data.description:
Welcome to your ideal urban oasis! This charming residence is strategically located just minutes from downtown; enjoy the city's bustling energy with a short commute to downtown, where you can explore top-notch restaurants, cultural attractions, and lively nightlife. Near the vibrant Tremont Area, embrace the unique character of the Tremont Area, known for its historic charm, art galleries, and eclectic dining options. It's a cultural hub right at your doorstep.
Easy Access to Highways commuting is a breeze with quick access to major highways, making reaching any part of the city or beyond convenient. Don't let this one get away! Schedule your private showing today!
